          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，张任。可恨刘备，带领人马夺取西川。是俺奉了主公之令，带兵把守雒城。\n众将官，起兵前往！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吹牌子，同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 3,
          "唱": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 1.0,
        "dominant_style_family": "西皮",
        "musical_styles": [
          "西皮摇板"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "张飞"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四下手引张飞同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，张飞。在帐中奉了军师将令，扮做樵夫模样，藏在芦苇之中，等候张任到\n来，定要擒他下马。\n三军的，就此前往！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 2,
          "白": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "张任",
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（八卦旗引诸葛亮同上，四龙套、四英雄引张任自下场门同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来者敢么是张任？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张任",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "然也。你是何人？敢挡某家去路！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "山人诸葛亮在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张任",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那刘玄德，与吾主乃是同宗兄弟，为何带领人马前来攻取西川？是何道理！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你主闇弱，不听忠言。吾主刘玄德统领仁义之师，重整汉室社稷。那曹操以百\n万之众，闻吾之名，望风丧胆，弃甲而逃。似你无名之辈，还不下马投降，等\n候何时？少时马前被擒，悔之晚矣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张任",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺乃堂堂大将，岂能降你？看枪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大胆！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张任退。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮下，众人随下。张任观察形势。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张任",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手引黄忠同上，起打，黄忠败下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套引魏延同上，起打，魏延败下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张任耍枪花，追下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "诸葛亮→张任",
          "turns": 4
