    {
      "scene_index": 9,
      "label": "第九场",
      "characters_present": [
        "张任",
        "张飞",
        "我本西蜀有名将",
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（八卦旗引诸葛亮同上，坐帐。黄忠、魏延、赵云、张飞同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张任拿到！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "绑上来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将张任绑上来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四下手押张任同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张任",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "大将失机入罗网，\n盖世英雄无下场！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胆大张任，见了山人为何不跪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张任",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺乃西蜀上将，岂肯跪你！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你既被擒，若肯归降我主，定是封侯之位。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张任",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某今被擒，你要杀就杀，要斩就斩，何必多言！若要叫俺归降，除非是日从西\n起！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张任",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怒气不息把话讲，\n诸葛孔明听端详：\n岂肯在此把你降！"
        },
        {
          "character": "我本西蜀有名将、诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "山人只把好言讲，\n大胆小儿敢逞狂。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞磨刀，斫，张任倒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然是忠义一儿郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张任忠心为主，执意不降。来，将他尸首不可损坏，用棺木盛殓，埋葬高坡，\n以表忠义。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众下手抬张任同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "后帐排宴，与众位将军贺功！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
